Package: ChIPbinner
Title: This package is designed for analyzing binned ChIP-seq or Cut&Run data for broad histone marks
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Reinnier", "Padilla", , "reinnier.padilla@mail.mcgill.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package will analyze binned ChIP-seq/Cut&Run data. You can visualize genome-wide changes using this software and subsequently analyze clusters of similarly-behaving genomic regions.
